          %div.act_desc 　AP、消費EN、特殊1、特殊2、旋回速度、防御属性、防御値、金額、弾薬費、重量
    %tbody.closed
      %tr
        %td.indent
        %td= f.label :ap_form, 'AP'
        %td.formNum= text_field_tag :ap_form, @ap_form
        %td= f.label :spending_en_form, '消費EN'
        %td.formNum= text_field_tag :spending_en_form, @spending_en_form
      %tr
        %td.indent
